src:
MFBTY drop trippy animated MV teaser for 'Dream Catcher'
07 Nov 2019, 09:35 by germainej
MFBTY have dropped a trippy animated MV teaser for their upcoming release "Dream Catcher".The MV teaser reveals a trippy, hip hop theme with animated versions of Tiger JK, Yoon Mi Rae, and Bizzy as well as an interesting beat featuring a lot of brass. MFBTY's "Dream Catcher" drops on November 10 KST. Stay tuned for updates!
